title: Marillion - Complete DVDRip Pack (As Of 2013) x264 - Anonymous
description:
Marillion - Complete DVDRip Pack (As Of 2013) x264 - Anonymous

All videos have been re-encoded with x264 (original resolution/framerate, constant quality 22 RF).
Original AC3/DTS audio has been kept with maximum channels. PCM 2.0 audio (if only available) has been converted to AC3 192 kbit/s.
All the DVD extras are also included!
